{"tid":2180467,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【Respect】韋根破產求助 愛心球星疑匿名捐五萬","createTime":"2020-08-30T01:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T13:50:41.000Z","uid":165817,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3cb51c42bb1b10e58487f76a9e0e79ab79f39e","tid":2180467,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:10:06.000Z","msg":"英甲球會韋根因經營不善，現正處於托管階段，面臨破產。如果球季開始時仍然無法找到接盤人收購，球會有可能需要解散。<br />\n<br />\n韋根球迷在網上發起「Save Our Club」眾籌活動，嘗試拯救愛隊，豈料活動疑似獲得一位從未效力過韋根的國腳級球星響應。<br />\n<br />\n一名球迷在 Twitter 上聯絡了格拉斯哥流浪前鋒迪科爾 (Jermain Defoe)，請求後者施予援手，捐贈五千英鎊（折合約五萬二千港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmdJT9o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmdJT9o.jpg&h=7ab29b15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事緣在二零零九年，迪科爾所屬的熱刺主場九比一血洗韋根，迪科爾個人轟入五球，成為英超歷史上單場入球最多的球員。有韋根球迷覺得，迪科爾應該為此作出補償。<br />\n<br />\n豈料，這個半開玩笑的請求竟然獲得迪科爾低調回應。不久後，一筆五千英鎊的匿名捐款被存入該基金。球迷們相信，這筆捐款來自迪科爾，甚至有球迷希望迪科爾能夠成為韋根部分股份的持有人，或在球會找到買家前為他們提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2gGFP9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2gGFP9.jpg&h=4a8128cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韋根去季因財務問題被扣十二分，最後以兩分之差護級失敗，他們的未來仍未確定，目前亦沒有官方證實，迪科爾是這名匿名捐款人。<br />\n<br />\n迪科爾是球壇著名的愛心大使。年僅六歲的新特蘭球迷路維利 (Bradley Lowery) 患癌後，迪科爾主動接觸該名男童及其家人，在治療期間一直給予心靈和經濟上的援助。在路維利過世後，迪科爾多次在記者會和喪禮上痛哭，更把路維利的名字紋上手臂紀念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vstqn1X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVstqn1X.jpg&h=e50e1b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n迪科爾對慈善不遺餘力的貢獻，令他在兩年前獲頒大英帝國勳章，使他與碧咸 (David Beckham)、雲加 (Arsene Wenger) 及卜比摩亞 (Bobby Moore) 等球壇傑出人士齊名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcO57vz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcO57vz.jpg&h=f26c9ca3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1f50380136f6685f2ea7eb7d61baf4ca796b97d","tid":2180467,"uid":114217,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:27:07.000Z","msg":"收到風<br />\n其實係連加特捐"},{"pid":"9dfe63c19fcbb97459891f967f2b27328b611cfa","tid":2180467,"uid":19126,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"迪科爾本身形象都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da8ea06eb901abdd1f25bf967b4daa8b97b00c8","tid":2180467,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:34:42.000Z","msg":"俾香港人班主搞到破產降班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人眾籌！<br />\n<br />\n毅進星 $100"},{"pid":"c29b3e7ce0eb9937d3cdfca2a71306622b9690f9","tid":2180467,"uid":309002,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:35:41.000Z","msg":"香港人投資英國波<br />\n <br />\n伯明翰 韋根都無好下場"},{"pid":"72861de88d345c984a5d46cfad9a6a2c049001bf","tid":2180467,"uid":149607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比人咁樣叫捐錢佢都捐"},{"pid":"5777b39e80a9c28d928082b226d82e950d69cc61","tid":2180467,"uid":116510,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UqdRiOy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUqdRiOy.png&h=78a9e672&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae8d05bfd63a0ffd0d0151d01efe09c35ffb9a59","tid":2180467,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:43:55.000Z","msg":"小強都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2438c3b3a7661024e9a1a8a66a3a05986c18d9","tid":2180467,"uid":182927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"慘，要上身"},{"pid":"cae12b40801d548c70fcf3b0d945ea4a6303da4d","tid":2180467,"uid":308251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:47:43.000Z","msg":"球迷們相信，這筆捐款來自迪科爾<br />\n<br />\n講咁多原來係同連登班ff撚一樣"},{"pi